Look at <a href="http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_40_0/doc/html/boost/mpi/intercommunicator.html">http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_40_0/doc/html/boost/mpi/intercommunicator.html</a><br>to have a Boost wrapper for an Intercommunicator.<br>
